                    <span class="toc-line"></span>
                    <span>4</span>
                </div>
                <div class="toc-item">
                    <span class="font-medium">3. El Proceso de Reclutamiento</span>
                    <span class="toc-line"></span>
                    <span>6</span>
                </div>
                <div class="toc-item">
                    <span class="font-medium">4. huntU - Inteligencia Artificial en Reclutamiento</span>
                    <span class="toc-line"></span>
                    <span>8</span>
                </div>
                <div class="toc-item">
                    <span class="font-medium">5. Amigro</span>
